# JOB FINDR 
## Description
- This repository contains the backend code for the Job Board application.
- The backend is implemented with ExpressJS, MongoDB, and Mongoose.
- providing RESTful API endpoints for user authentication, job listings, and applications.


## Instructions to Run this App Locally:
###  1- Clone the Repository in your VS Code:
- git clone https://github.com/JOB-FINDR/job-findr-frontend 


### 2- Install Dependencies:
- npm install

### 3- Run the Application:
- npm run dev

### 4- Environment Variables:
Create a .env file in the root of the backend directory and 
save the API URL in this format -- 
- PORT=5005
- ORIGIN=http://localhost:5173
- TOKEN_SECRET=y0uRt0k3N$eCr3T

## Demo
Visit https://job-findr-api.adaptable.app  to test the API.

